{"tid":1570120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾警隊返工hea做真人真事事件","createTime":"2019-09-15T02:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:27:27.000Z","uid":271009,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4cebdf82f28c05feaf86c3672caeb0bc16d03de","tid":1570120,"uid":271009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"個幾月前，試過打999熱線中心報警話見到有私家車違例逆線行車衝燈，差d撞到途人，但係太突然冇片做證據，但提供到車牌號碼比999，電話到叫黑警問附近商戶調查, 因為附近見到有CCTV 個cam面向馬路, 又唔派黑警到案發現場。熱線中心問有冇人受傷，冇人受傷便話要交比交通警察個邊跟進。之後留低聯絡資料後幾日，交警個邊打電話返來。我叫佢地去調查違例行車事件，佢地竟然好hea 問左幾句：有冇片，有冇人受傷。我答冇。之後我叫佢地去調查，提供埋車牌號碼。佢地竟然係冇意慾去調查，話會打電話比個車主了解下事件，警告下佢就算。違法不去調查而係由佢當冇件事，就係hk黑警做法。"},{"pid":"f884095c6c47c7f50867029aff10ace84b30cd07","tid":1570120,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK, Anti-totalitarianism March on 29/9/2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"723a618c5864582fac374832a41c0497528e3ce7","tid":1570120,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"佢地宜家大Q哂架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，鍾意做就做"},{"pid":"a7f33163149edade73848214136e189f1f7f6f9d","tid":1570120,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:16:33.000Z","msg":"公開秘密   過街警鼠做野一向斷鳩估<br />\n<br />\n香港差佬呢  就黑暗醜惡   <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff38419c6c6c04a2d2b5fd51a3e49aa08980927","tid":1570120,"uid":108814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"犯罪率低 因為全部放走哂 香港克警又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6112441833444bbdf560033c5cd6e44abbf395","tid":1570120,"uid":242851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"